'''Willy Ndahiro''' ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwanda]] wavukiye i [[bujumbura]], mu [[Burundi]] iya 1, mata 1976, yamenyekanye nka Paul muri filimi [[Rwanda|nyarwanda]] yakunzwe  cyane <nowiki>''Ikigeragezo cy' ubuzima", Ni umuyobozi ndetse n'</nowiki>umukinnyi wa filimi [[Rwanda|nyarwanda]] kuva 2006<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/filmmaker-ndahiro-unveils-new-film-production-studio</ref>.<ref>http://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/willy-ndahiro-agiye-gusohora-filime-igaragaramo-umuhanzi-ngarambe-francois</ref>  Byatumye aba umuyobozi wa komite ishinze abakinnyi bamafilimi mu [[Rwanda]] mu mwaka wa 2014-2015, ubu akaba ari umuyobozi w'urugaga [[Rwanda|nyarwanda]] rureberera abakora umwuga wa Cinema mu [[Rwanda]] (Rwanda Film Federation). <ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/70010/umukinnyi-wa-filime-willy-ndahiro-aramaganira-kure-ibihuha-b-70010.html</ref>. Zimwe muri filimi yayoboye akanakinamo ni "Ay'urukundo"," Kanyarwanda","Anitha" na "Ikigeragezo cy'ubuzima".<ref>https://genesisbizz.com/Willy-Ndahiro-yagizwe-umuyobozi-mukuru-wa-Rwanda-Film-Federation-w-agateganyo</ref>

== Ubuzima bwa Willy muri make ==
Willy Ndahiro yavukiye mu [[Burundi]] muri 1976, muri 1993 yaje mu [[Rwanda]] yinjira mu gisirikare cya Rwanda Patriotic Army (APR) afatanya n'abandi guhagarika [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenocide yakorewe abatutsi muri 1994]], nyuma yakomereje akazi mu ngabo zirinda perezida kugeza 2004.<ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/147647</ref> <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/rwanda-today/lifestyle/movie-industry-needs-more-money-1311272</ref>Willy avuye mu gisirikare yasubiye kwiga mu gihugu cy'u [[Burundi]] aho yari yaracirkirije amashuri ye arangiriza mu bijyanye n'indimi(Lettreture), muri 2006 nibwo yatangiye inzira yo gukina filimi atangirira kuri filimi yahise ituma amenyekana "Ikigeragezo cy'ubuzima"<ref>https://kglnews.com/index.php/tag/willy-ndahiro/</ref>, muri 2010 yayoboye ndetse akina muyindi filimi yakunzwe cyane "Ay'urukundo"<ref>https://umuseke.rw/paul-wo-mu-kigeragezo-cyubuzima-azabenguka-mushiki-we-muri-film-bazanyemo.html</ref>. Willy kandi yagiye ashinga studio zitunganya amafilimi harimo iyakoze filmi nyinshi yitwa"Vision Production Ltd"<ref>https://ibyamamare.com/ndahiro-natacha-umukobwa-ufite-amafoto-akunzwe-cyane-mbuga-nkoranyambaga-kubera-uburanga-bwe-agiye-gusohora-filime-yakinanye-na-musaza-we/</ref> Willy NDAHIRO ubu ni umuyobozi wa Rwanda Film Federation ,rukaba ari urugaga [[Rwanda|nyarwanda]] ruhuza abakora umwuga wa Cinema mu [[Rwanda]].

